</subtitle><entry><title type="html">Nucleosomes and conveyors</title><link href="https://shi-why.github.io/blog/2023/formatting-and-links/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nucleosomes and conveyors" /><published>2023-09-15T16:40:16+00:00</published><updated>2023-09-15T16:40:16+00:00</updated><id>https://shi-why.github.io/blog/2023/formatting-and-links</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://shi-why.github.io/blog/2023/formatting-and-links/"><![CDATA[<p>The structure of nucleosomes in chromatin has been given a very interesting analogy-</p>

<p>“The beads on a string” appearance:</p>
