<p>But can this structural analogy explain the function of the nucleosome?
In this post, I will show you how to imagine, what the actual function of the nucleosome is in our DNA.</p>

<p>For this, I want you to imagine our DNA was a conveyor belt(literally!).</p>
<div class="row mt-3">
    <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0" style="max-width: 40%">
        <figure>

  <picture>
    
    <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/image2-480.webp" />
